"{\"uid\": \"thehollywoodgossip.com-2024-07-jodie-sweetin-defends-olympics-drag-after-candace-cameron-bure\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByAuthorKay Rhodes  Published:Jul 29, 2024 at 3:53 PM \\u2022Updated:Aug 05, 2024 at 11:38 AM \\u2022CategoryCandace Cameron  Reading Time:3minutes  For not the first time, TV sister Jodie Sweetin and Candace Cameron Bure find themselves on very different sides of an issue.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 171, \"end\": 184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jodie_Sweetin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jodie Sweetin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jodie_Sweetin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jodie_Sweetin\"}, {\"begin\": 189, \"end\": 209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Candace Cameron Bure\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\"}, {\"begin\": 205, \"end\": 209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Bure\", \"score\": 0.9976975668603512, \"rank\": 0.00230774656463559, \"text\": \"Bure\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Bure\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following theParis Olympics Opening Ceremony, Candace posted her \\\"disgust\\\" over a particular section involving drag queens.\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"score\": 0.9999999990222932, \"rank\": 6.395170285078116e-10, \"text\": \"Candace\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To her, the performance as an affront to her Christian faith.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 433, \"end\": 442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9996274005036639, \"rank\": 0.00037273375777859024, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite reassurances from theOlympicscommittee, Candace has stirred up a fury of rage from her community  - but also, a flurry of defense from those who do not agree with her indignation.\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 499, \"end\": 506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"score\": 0.9999999990222932, \"rank\": 6.395170285078116e-10, \"text\": \"Candace\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enter Stephanie Tanner to say, in a way, \\\"HOW RUDE!\\\"\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 692, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While it's very well documented that Candace is a Christian, so it is understood that Jodie is a fervent LGBTQ activist and ally.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"score\": 0.9999999990222932, \"rank\": 6.395170285078116e-10, \"text\": \"Candace\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\"}, {\"begin\": 744, \"end\": 753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9996274005036639, \"rank\": 0.00037273375777859024, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it should come as no surprise that Jodie seemingly clapped back at her formerFull Housecostar after the former criticized the now controversial drag show during the 2024 Olympics opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In posts over the weekend on Instagram, Candace spurned the performance which she believed was a recreation of Leonardo da Vinci's painting of \\\"The Last Supper\\\".\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1055, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.020504394257975e-28, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"score\": 0.9999999990222932, \"rank\": 6.395170285078116e-10, \"text\": \"Candace\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\"}, {\"begin\": 1137, \"end\": 1154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2627687377306804e-23, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She called it \\\"completely blasphemous\\\" and downright \\\"disgusting\\\".\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then, organizers have insisted that in fact, the performance was a depiction of a painting called 'Feast of the Gods' by Johann Rottenhammer.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1384, \"end\": 1390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Strauss_II\", \"score\": 0.9929597884905095, \"rank\": 0.006721386204365522, \"text\": \"Johann\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Strauss_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Strauss_II\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Candace refused to accept this explanation and carried on ranting about how inappropriate it all was, others stepped in to play devil's advocate.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1411, \"end\": 1418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"score\": 0.9999999990222932, \"rank\": 6.395170285078116e-10, \"text\": \"Candace\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by matt bernstein (@mattxiv)  That when Jodie shared anInstagramgallery to her stories from influencer Matt Bernstein's account highlighting the comparisons and frankly, the hypocrisy of it all.\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bernstein\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"matt bernstein\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bernstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bernstein\"}, {\"begin\": 1675, \"end\": 1689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bernstein\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Bernstein\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bernstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bernstein\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The drag queens at the olympics were re-creating the feast of Dionysus, not the last supper,\\\" he wrote on the post Jodi shared.\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1831, \"end\": 1839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3007820269613444e-18, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And even if you thought it was a christian reference - what's the harm?\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1970, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why is it a parody and not a tribute?\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Can drag queens not be christian too?\\\"\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2047, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris Olympics2024 organizers reacted to the backlash the opening ceremony received on Sunday, July 28, offering apologies to anyone who was offended by the drag-filled performance onX(formerlyTwitter).\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2251, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That apparently wasn't good enough for Candace.\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2292, \"end\": 2299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"score\": 0.9999999990222932, \"rank\": 6.395170285078116e-10, \"text\": \"Candace\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Cameron_Bure\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Since posting, many have tried to correct me saying it wasn't about an interpretation of DaVinci's The Last Supper, but a Greek god and the festival of Dionysus,\\\" she saidin a poston Monday morning.\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2392, \"end\": 2399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.078771522127742e-23, \"text\": \"DaVinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 2402, \"end\": 2417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Last_Supper\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.453719179420987e-24, \"text\": \"The Last Supper\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Last_Supper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Last_Supper\"}, {\"begin\": 2455, \"end\": 2463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3007820269613444e-18, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pointing to Dionysus' being the \\\"god of lust, insanity, religious ecstasy,\\\" among other things, she insisted that the performance was unacceptable \\\"for children to watch.\\\"\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2515, \"end\": 2523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3007820269613444e-18, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In any case, I am not buying it,\\\" she added, rebuking the committee's assurances.\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In her Instagram, she carried on:  \\\"It made me so sad, and someone said, 'You should not be sad.\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2767, \"end\": 2776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.020504394257975e-28, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You should be mad about it.'\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am like, 'Trust me, it makes me mad, but I am more sad because I am sad for souls.'\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I pray for my heart to break over what breaks God's heart and I just think about all the people that have rejected the gospel of Jesus Christ or do not know the gospel of Jesus Christ,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 3170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3103, \"end\": 3115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999996939450753, \"rank\": 3.060551866623695e-07, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}, {\"begin\": 3145, \"end\": 3157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999996939450753, \"rank\": 3.060551866623695e-07, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Erica Ash, Survivor's Remorse and MADtv Alum, Dead at 46  Donald Trump Shades Miley Cyrus For Billy Ray's Sake in Bizarre Speech\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3172, \"end\": 3181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erica_Ash\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Erica Ash\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erica_Ash\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erica_Ash\"}, {\"begin\": 3230, \"end\": 3242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999554348, \"rank\": 4.430069018254085e-11, \"text\": \"Don